    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Sudden severe leg pain\nSwelling and edema (bleb/bullae)\nCyanosis\nVenous gangrene\nCompartment syndrome\nArterial compromise\nShock\nOften preceded by\nphlegmasia alba dolens",
